name: March 7th (Honkai Star Rail)/三月七
description:
Full trigger words : ph_Mar,Marhd, Mards, 1girl, solo, skirt, gloves, earrings, jewelry, bangs, blue eyes, pink eyes, black gloves, long sleeves, blue skirt, choker, fingerless gloves, white shirt, hair between eyes, short hair, single glove, pleated skirt, partially fingerless gloves, purple eyes, jacket, multicolored eyes

Necessary trigger words : ph_Mar, Marhd, Mards, 1girl, solo, jewelry, blue eyes, pink eyes, hair between eyes, short hair, purple eyes, multicolored eyes

if you want to change the outfit, use necessary trigger words only and add the prompt words for the clothing you want to (as far as it exist in your ckpt)

Notice：As before, this lora was based on Meinaalter——https://civitai.com/models/20945/meinaalter

if your outputs are undesirable, try this ckpt or others high compatibility ANIME base model, because while the base model without some concepts of my trigger word, then the Ai can't draw them well. waiting for your comments and ❤ ※ (*>.<*)~

Here I will explain why I don't use Nai as the base model for training. Indeed, using Nai as the base model can greatly improve generalization of basemodel while generating and ensure that the maximum number of clothing on the body learns details, but training with no Anime specific base molds can produce output that often deviates slightly from Anime style, which is not what I want. I would rather sacrifice some flexibility in exchange for the results more than close to anime style. That is. Thanks for understanding.

Notice：The characters are copyrighted by miHoYo, this lora for exchange leaning only, do not use for commercial purposes and improper use.

所有触发词：ph_Mar, Marhd, Mards, 1girl, solo, skirt, gloves, earrings, jewelry, bangs, blue eyes, pink eyes, black gloves, long sleeves, blue skirt, choker, fingerless gloves, white shirt, hair between eyes, short hair, single glove, pleated skirt, partially fingerless gloves, purple eyes, jacket, multicolored eyes

必要触发词: ph_Mar, Marhd, Mards, 1girl, solo, jewelry, blue eyes, pink eyes, hair between eyes, short hair, purple eyes, multicolored eyes如果想要更换着装的话，用必要提示词提示词，加上你想要的服装提示词就行了（前提是你的底模型里有这种服装）

如果效果不好，请使用Meinaalter、Anything或其它适应性强的底模型，因为当底模型缺少我训练用到的概念时会无法绘制出相同的结果。喜欢的话给个评论和点赞吧❤ ※ (*>.<*)~

这里解释下为什么我使用二次元底模而非Nai训练的原因，诚然用Nai当作底模可以大大提高泛化度、生成图片时选择底模的多样性、以及可以最大程度学习到人物身上细节，但是使用非二次元专用底模训练往往会使生成结果略微偏移原本的二次元画风，这不是我想要的结果。因此我宁愿牺牲一部分灵活性来换取更二次元化的输出结果。（参考上面图片）

注意：角色版权归米哈游公司所有，本lora仅供交流学习，分享同人创作快乐，请勿用于商业用途与不正当用途。
